snippet.title: You'll MELT FROM CUTENESS and LAUGH FROM FUNNINESS - Best BABY ANIMAL videos
snippet.description:
Here are the funniest videos of baby animals! These baby animals are so super cute and funny! Bet you will die laughing! This is the hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these kittens, puppies, baby goat, cow, bunny, bear, donkey, lama, duck, chicken, monkeys,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
